  <div class="container my-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
      <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to EuroCup2024 InveStars!</h1>
      <p class="lead">Invest in your favorite teams and watch your points grow as they advance in the 2024 Euro Cup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-4">
      <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">Overview</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p>Buy stock in teams competing in the 2024 Euro Cup. When teams earn points you earn a percentage base on your equity in the team.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-4">
      <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">Investing</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <ul>
              <li>You have 100 credits available to invest in up to 6 teams.</li>
              <li>You cannot invest more than 50 credits in a single team.</li>
              <li>When the tournament starts you will no longer be allowed to edit your investments.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-4">
      <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">Points Breakdown</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body p-0">
            <table class="table ">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col">Result</th>
                  <th scope="col">Points</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <% Result.points_map.each do |result, points| %>
                  <tr>
                    <td><%= result %></td>
                    <td><%= points %></td>
                  </tr>
                <% end %>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mb-4">
      <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header bg-warning text-white">
            <h2 class="h5 mb-0">Tips</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p>Tournament favorites will likely have heavier investment by more players, meaning less equity for you.</p>
            <p>Consider investing in underdogs or wildcards, as they will likely have fewer investors, meaning better equity of their points.</p>
            <p>You may find yourself with 100% of a team's points if no one else invested.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>